This is precisely the progressive trust model: cached chains start at low trust (high , low coverage) and graduate to higher trust (lower , higher coverage) as the guarantee tightens with more data. The RCPS certificate makes this graduation formal: the system can provably state “with probability , the unsafe rate is at most ” at each trust level.
